{"type": "article", "id": 52615, "title": "一个球形首饰盒的七种打开方式｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-27T00:35:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 21587, "name": "Muuto"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 49737, "name": "Blanc Bijou"}, {"id": 49738, "name": "ABS Studio"}, {"id": 49560, "name": "Kettal"}, {"id": 49739, "name": "Ivan Goran Žunar"}, {"id": 49740, "name": "Jens Fager"}, {"id": 49741, "name": "Francesco Balzano"}, {"id": 49742, "name": "Valériane Lazard"}, {"id": 23568, "name": "Konstantin Grcic"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 194, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180426231212tP7c6SRL0FolJByu.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s7 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Meteo Sunshade by Konstantin Grcic for Kettal</h3><p>在今年的米兰家具展上，西班牙户外家具品牌 Kettal 推出了一款突破性新品 Meteo 遮阳伞，操刀设计的是柏林当红产品设计师 Konstantin Grcic。</p><p>这也是 Kettal 的第一款户外遮阳伞产品，伞部是棱角分明的几何结构。用 Konstantin Grcic 的话说，这是帮助 Kettal 进入“微型建筑”（micro-architecture）领域的第一步。Kettal 目前正在考虑扩大产品范围，而不仅仅是制造家具。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231413LXOCNHvil9tPy5z0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231413nlNCWO6vytZXo2uD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.731429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231414S42yBlR59m8ceOfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.307500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804262314130h2b3sTOSALkXPwY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.kettal.com/en/particular/blogpost/meteobykonstantingrcicen/P/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kettal</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The limited-edition Primitif Collection by Francesco Balzano and Valériane Lazard</h3><p>迈阿密 Studio Twenty Seven 画廊展出了限量版 Primitif 系列家具，是法国设计师 Francesco Balzano 和 ValérianeLazard 的联手之作，包括凳子、桌子、长凳、边桌、茶几、罐子、壁灯和纸镇。</p><p>每件作品均采用产自意大利的米黄色 Pietra di Medici 石灰石雕刻而成，因此它们都具有相似的纹理和色调。据设计师透露，这组作品是对英国巨石阵建筑遗址的致敬之作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231637rYkNH0iZ2ETpbzuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231642VIWcStvmgXE4wjrx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231642kAEcNzhsMCbQm9tx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231644TdR63hZxOkNEovyf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804262316440nbkfKBQC7qz9Jtd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231645w6TajbneftNZpgiB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231730UlgfEAJB4dtLHFD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/04/25/studio-twenty-seven-showcases-stone-furniture-italian-limestone-francesco-balzano-valeriane-lazard/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Moonlight by ABS Studio for EGOLUCE</h3><p>今年是意大利照明品牌 EGOLUCE 创立 40 周年，设计工作室 ABS 为其设计了一系列名为 Moonlight 的顶灯和壁灯，是大小不一的圆形组合，由中密度纤维板制成，分为三种不同强度的光源。</p><p>灯的前部面板上装饰有特殊饰面，可以选择不同漆面进行重新喷涂，较小尺寸的灯盘还有镜面光盘、金箔、银叶以及黑色饰面可供选择。多种选择允许用户对特定空间进行独特的个性化组合方式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231807EsyzLYrd2ZDtjHC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730612\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231812gv5Vk3L67MNqOHQ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.794558\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804262318121lIyHt62k7wdjGBQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732606\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231816Ckg9URu8Pc4mxaNK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.834925\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Seven Sliding Cases by Nendo for Blanc Bijou</h3><p>含氟聚合物是一种通过压缩和加热颗粒状的天然氟石而形成的分子材料，特点是高度的耐久性、耐磨性和防污性能，因此能够长时间地保持完好无损的外观。</p><p>最近，日本设计工作室 Nendo 为 Blanc Bijou 公司设计的首饰盒系列，设计就源自于对含氟聚合物的研究和应用。闭合时，每款首饰盒都有着相同的直径为 65 毫米的球形外观，而其内部却设有不同的机关。这些机关决定了每个盒子的打开方式，通过不同的滑动方法，盒子内的首饰也将以独一无二的形式被呈现出来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231857ftNQ71gGL503U8Rz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804262319019Blqd7ki2Tn8awNj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231902bSphMXdarxcFRo42.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231902bmVMskjC8hqK1fGT.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231902hsQeIrUg2dkLmlA5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231903APjlzI7DWJbv9w0Y.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018042623190392xVz4fp5CkrOTyi.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426231904D57ytBsmWxlnijVv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Nendo</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Tip Lamp by Jens Fager for Muuto</h3><p>瑞典设计师 Jens Fager 认为，设计就是用城市的态度对待每一件产品，聚焦其主要功能的实现。这款丹麦设计品牌 Muuto 生产的 Tip 台灯，是他站在孩童视角出发的设计，摒弃所有复杂的形势，专注于细节和功能。</p><p>横平竖直的铝制灯架，搭配一个微微扬起头的灯罩和圆形灯座，共同构成了干净利落的外观，就像孩子们眼中看到的那些美丽、清爽、纯净的事物一样，不会对它的功能、结构产生疑惑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232009j3Etz6OSosAHPpy8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.348125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232009UBj2YDFOETi7awhR.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232010b1J9zmWNAyrGjfoq.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232010gWM0ZKOI5kGnA3uU.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232012Itn3QVGEy6ruBdWJ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.232500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://muuto.com/lighting/tip-lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Muuto</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>SecretArea by Ivan Goran Žunar</h3><p>在公司，你可能偶尔会需要一个不受周围环境干扰的空间，以便于专注于自己的案头工作。克罗地亚设计师 Ivan Goran Žunar 提出了一种名为 SecretArea 的解决方案，考虑到实用功能之外，也兼顾了视觉上的有趣美感。</p><p>一个类似茧形的结构，既起到了隔离空间的作用，又将文具、电缆、电话、记事本和其它杂物收纳在缝隙中，避免了桌面的杂乱无章。桌面下方的两层抽屉也提供了充足的收纳小物的空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804262321553NunzH540RLhI2ep.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232155IkehswjOz0NoSAuH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232157cOIkpuAt2D7TNKGw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232158T9uvXS52LPpcrCbE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180426232158rqpYDm4AhKRduNwg.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/04/25/distraction-free-working/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}